

--- wallpaper ---
zoxenpher has tiled wallpaper support. You can choose a wallpaper using a cnf.dat setting.
1Note: read configuration help first!	/	about:help_conf	70

 -Set to 'none' for no wallpaper.
bgtile=none

using your own wallpaper:
place the wallpaper image in the 'usr' directory (where cnf.example and cnf.dat are)
then set bgtile to the filename of the image. i.e. bgtile=example.jpg

you can also select from the included wallpapers in the following gallery:

example: 'bgtile=tilebg.png'


gallery:
p'tilebg.png'	/	about:tilebg.png	70
p'tilebg2.png'	/	about:tilebg2.png	70
p'mascotbg.png'	/	about:mascotbg.png	70
p'diagbg.png'	/	about:diagbg.png	70




1Return to configuration help	/	about:help_conf	70
1Return to help menu	/	about:help	70